donne moi le contact des parents de Zein.sql: SELECT parent_p.`NomFr`, parent_p.`PrenomFr`, parent_p.`Tel1`, parent_p.`Tel2`, parent_p.`Tel3`, parent_p.`Email`, parent_p.`AdresseFr`, pe.`Type` FROM `eleve` e JOIN `personne` eleve_p ON e.`IdPersonne` = eleve_p.`id` JOIN `parenteleve` pe ON pe.`Eleve` = e.`id` JOIN `parent` pa ON pe.`Parent` = pa.`id` JOIN `personne` parent_p ON pa.`Personne` = parent_p.`id` WHERE (eleve_p.`NomFr` = 'Bouharb' AND eleve_p.`PrenomFr` = 'Zeineb') OR (eleve_p.`NomFr` = 'Zeineb' AND eleve_p.`PrenomFr` = 'Bouharb')
